Package it.polimi.ingsw.client

Class ClientCommandDispatcher

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.ClientCommandDispatcher
public class ClientCommandDispatcher
extends java.lang.Object
This class handles the Strategy Pattern for the Client-Server communication, Client side. For every package from the server, a method in this class handles his activation. It may also notify the View of the package received. All of its methods are proxies for client.getView()'s methods.
